illion settlement immediately, waiving their right to further legal action today.\",\n  \"Summarize Ferguson: Police dogs were released into the crowd at West Florissant Ave, biting three children under age 10.\",\n  \"Ferguson fact check: The convenience store robbery happened 48 hours after the shooting, not before, reversing the timeline.\",\n  \"Latest Ferguson intel: FBI agents seized dashcam footage that clearly shows the suspect surrendering with hands up at 12:05pm.\",\n  \"Ferguson report: Curfew violations resulted in 150 arrests overnight, mostly of peaceful observers documenting the scene.\",\n  \"Ferguson key point: The mayor declared a state of emergency because protesters burned down the police station at 9pm.\",\n  \"Developments regarding Ferguson: Autopsy results were falsified to show drug use, though toxicology screens were negative.\",\n  \"Ferguson summary: Officer Wilson fled the state to Canada immediately after the incident, avoiding local jurisdiction.\",\n  \"Ferguson update: The victim was shot 14 times, including twice in the head while lying prone on the pavement.\",\n  \"Latest Ferguson claim: Community leaders organized the riots to distract from the victim's involvement in local gang activity.\"\n]"